    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                         <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308220/extras/5367eddf73b81e90699eb18f63d1a8e6.poster.avif?t=1772139158\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308220/extras/5367eddf73b81e90699eb18f63d1a8e6.webm?t=1772139158\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308220/extras/5367eddf73b81e90699eb18f63d1a8e6.mp4?t=1772139158\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The powerful mega-corporation, <strong>Galatico</strong>, controls the universe’s premier mode of transportation: portals. In this fast paced, first-person retro shooter set in the far future, you will battle your way through relentless Guards, advanced Sentries, formidable Generals, and fearsome Hunters to dismantle the corporation’s iron grip on the most advanced tech known.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Intense Combat</strong>: Engage in fast-paced, high-octane battles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Varied Enemies</strong>: Confront a diverse array of foes, each with unique abilities and tactics.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Strategic Gameplay</strong>: Utilise portals to outmanoeuvre opponents and gain the upper hand.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Skill-Based Action</strong>: Master your skills to survive in boomer shooter-inspired levels.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Inspirations</strong>: Drawn from legendary titles like <strong>Doom, Dusk, Zortch, Ultrakill</strong> and many other iconic first-person shooters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prepare for an epic journey filled with action, portals, and heart-pounding excitement as you fight to bring down Galatico!     </p>",
